Hello, everybody.

00:00:03.900 --> 00:00:07.210
Let's talk some design affordances, all right?

00:00:07.260 --> 00:00:09.550
If you haven't met me, I'm Tynan

00:00:09.650 --> 00:00:09.810
.

00:00:09.810 --> 00:00:13.730
